            [1] = {
                ["language"] = "CN",
                ["body"] = "<div data-page-id=\"U4AjdrcSOoF5Wmxf2qocrVU7ndc\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnA0WVIdvuQcP8NVymjwlOvd\"><strong><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_吟游诗集活动开放-CHS.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></strong></h3>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnA0WVIdvuQcP8NVymjwlOvd\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>★【晨曦序曲】上架★&nbsp;</strong></span></h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnQq1Tk4ZgbkkwRzWaGpB66p\">※ 解锁【典藏诗集】即可获得「流年自选形象礼箱&middot;匆匆」*1!</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcncbMBtx2dnBR6DwTpI135qW\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcngLIO1AHX61nbDEZb9zppcc\"><strong>【开启时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn6I7AXwYNjtxe9fWzqiAoQd\"><strong>晨曦序曲I：</strong>2026年2月10日更新后 ~ 2026年3月10日 04:59 （UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn3VdVxRixpBpHPNda8DZimf\"><strong>晨曦序曲II：</strong>2026年3月10日 05:00 ~ 2026年4月7日 04:59（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcns9LaqfZM9kMeyVTjuU6qAg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcniwype2uggPFJLTfzj913ec\"><strong>【吟游诗集说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnxjarOBKzpZF2zVqqMdISce\">&bull; 活动期间，狩月人可通过完成吟游诗集的见闻任务提升诗歌段落等级，领取丰厚奖励。每期吟游诗集开启后，将默认解锁平装诗集。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnEuxR2dtuh1DzbH2ibJrGLd\">&bull; 解锁【精装诗集】并提升诗歌段落等级可获得「自选魔灵」、「月石」、「华彩沙漏」、「移转模块」、「武器移转模块」、「暮夜的履迹」、「委托手册」、「深红凝珠」等奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn0TgbSx5Qow1mrUJHiMteTe\">&bull; 解锁【典藏诗集】，除以上奖励外，可立即提升10级诗歌段落等级，还可额外获得「月石」*200、「委托手册&middot;三」*5以及「流年自选形象礼箱&middot;匆匆」*1奖励！</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Gh9FdhSfjot0MJxw5o1cGIi0n7g\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QGIndHPZEoqQuBxpJT3cVmfOngb\"><strong>【额外赠送说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TypKdA5qlo8T7Rxf8bWcnvl4nqg\">购买【精装诗集】与【典藏诗集】将额外获得《云&middot;二重螺旋》畅玩卡时长</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VVfHdYC8to5wQIxrnb6c6LfFn2c\">【精装诗集】：赠21天畅玩卡</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CGzqdFjKBojo5GxAqOxclIFbnoc\">【典藏诗集】：赠42天畅玩卡</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NiQAdPa3koZRSrx5Ohqc9uOYnBg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnvIAGEGZWhlNVOk4YmL4VIh\"><strong>【当前限定奖励说明】：</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KFOPdrcWboRUHFxDWcQcfcG3n5e\">吟游诗集将产出以下限定奖励</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OcAWdPSKQoxMbyxARUsc3hAHnKf\"><strong>晨曦序曲I：</strong>「头像&middot;呐喊」「展示动作&middot;转动螺旋」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VS8Adx4K9oK9Z0xiRvbc7A9in3g\"><strong>晨曦序曲II：</strong>「头像&middot;快乐起飞」「展示动作&middot;慷慨解囊」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Cle9dKbBJoiY0ZxKEi0cj9PAnzF\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnjZHa1aoX0iodRbSLBDtqgc\"><strong>【昨日匆匆自选形象奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnxZjUbbrnxlBI4g1Zu9jlhe\">获得形象自选箱后，可在【背包】-【消耗品】中开启，</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcns20c4yquf7kGj8rTRyWHkc\">开启时可从止流、煜明、扶疏、刻舟、贝蕾妮卡、幻景、莉兹贝尔、妮弗尔夫人、菲娜、丽蓓卡、塔比瑟、琳恩、耶尔与奥利弗、海尔法、玛尔洁、黎瑟、兰迪、西比尔、松露与榛子、奥特赛德、赛琪、达芙涅中自选一套角色形象。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcngFoCxLMtCuEUmDeouGLCie\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn4IuAjm8mf6LIfy5NEdUP2b\"><strong>【自选魔灵奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn41OojC7979QkOaPzXahVMh\">吟游诗集达到30级并解锁【精装诗集】或【典藏诗集】，可从以下五星魔灵中自选召唤一只：「堇青艾尔芙」、「碧玺艾尔芙」、「玛瑙艾尔芙」、「紫晶艾尔芙」、「黑曜艾尔芙」、「欧泊艾尔芙」。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnRMfj1U42DKQTQEZh6TeUxc\">召唤魔灵后，可在【整备】-【魔灵】界面进行查看和装配。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnRMfj1U42DKQTQEZh6TeUxc\">&nbsp;</div