lass=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcncjjGYRZd916f5A3H3WI6pe\"><strong>【礼包上架时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnesEddpCpgnbx916OKiTiMb\">2026年2月10日更新后 ~ 2026年4月6日 16:30（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn5XaaEgVXR9AenEBZdyrrCc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcncwPYsj3VPMv5rxxJ6zNq0H\"><strong>【礼包说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnZFa0t7sqXZZTW9rQWRwcOi\">活动期间【商店】将上架【<strong>华宴万华礼箱</strong>】、【<strong>鸣金万华礼箱</strong>】、<strong>【鸣金万华补给礼箱】、【鸣金装饰补给礼箱】</strong>。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnXVbkzcdMIZCQLxwCdlAZLc\">购买后可获得「华彩沙漏&middot;限时」以及其他道具奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnhp8b57EcXaAgmWhouFGtxh\">本期系列礼包中购买的「华彩沙漏&middot;限时」可用于在【宴夜诉平生】中进行寻觅，【宴夜诉平生】活动结束后将转换为「纯白沙漏」。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TH19d6cgbooYU4x2UToc20DanEf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DeuGdVJC5o8AGLxhsCDc7pXMnMc\"><strong>【额外赠送说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Tmg0dK5LioOO5ex8sSWcpIB3nWd\">购买以下礼包将额外获得《云&middot;二重螺旋》畅玩卡时长</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnc6owS8dnzco6ZWfwMxGAKh\">【鸣金装饰补给礼箱&middot;一】：赠3天畅玩卡 【鸣金装饰补给礼箱&middot;二】：赠7天畅玩卡</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnc6owS8dnzco6ZWfwMxGAKh\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnGbAw4s7oYlYbJQeyJprsHK\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnGbAw4s7oYlYbJQeyJprsHK\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_公告皎皎的订单-简中.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnGbAw4s7oYlYbJQeyJprsHK\">\n<div data-page-id=\"U4AjdrcSOoF5Wmxf2qocrVU7ndc\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnzVKz3JMaGKmGItHAOIRheN\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>★</strong>【侍者皎皎的月度订单】说明<strong>★</strong></span></h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnY1LQn7MwRDEwhe6eqdv4Th\">&bull; 首次购买「侍者皎皎的月度订单」可立即获得当期专属头像框、300月石晶胚、1本委托手册&middot;四，同时订单签约生效时间延长30日。重复购买可增加30天签约时长，在新的一期「月度订单」开启后若签约有效时间大于等于30天，将会获得新一期的「月度订单」限定头像框。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnUHInGUsTd0fJW6iJ7Xdh5c\">&bull; 在订单生效期间，每日登录游戏可领取90月石，2本委托手册&middot;二，每日凌晨5点重置。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PXRudeIHRoRvxFxsRDscpHRdnye\">&bull; 在订单生效期间，每日登录《云&middot;二重螺旋》可领取10小时的免费时长，每日凌晨5点重置。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnJOIKS2AyZwmTauBPhUpjCf\">&bull; 在订单生效期间，因为未登录游戏而未领取的月石、委托手册，不会返还。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn7zGTHaOJvaSdvBD9CxaP7b\">&bull; 月度订单的签约生效时间小于90天时，才可继续购买并正常增加生效时长。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-T9KXdxYLNoeZZfxokUicG07qnec\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
