                ["body"] = "<div data-page-id=\"Gudwdu5GooDZcFxV6FNcLygSndf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-I5XSdD5FrovRwKxvZZ1cJcdanHh\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_机傀大乱斗-简中.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-I5XSdD5FrovRwKxvZZ1cJcdanHh\"><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77);\">自古以来，总有人因为各种毫无关系的人物谁强谁弱而争得面红耳赤。现在，托公尚师傅的福，人们终于不用再引经据典地比拼强弱，而是可以直接通过这些拟真机傀在棋盘上的胜负，来获得一个定论。</span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ScKmdOPmXo78qUx1WeJcmlvEneb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnRUYcAjso946Wo9zIExAMDc\"><strong>【活动时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BYA1dTNuGorSEcx08lVcil2Nn9c\">2026年2月10日更新后 ~ 2026年4月6日 17:00（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BYA1dTNuGorSEcx08lVcil2Nn9c\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BYA1dTNuGorSEcx08lVcil2Nn9c\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Gudwdu5GooDZcFxV6FNcLygSndf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnPmmXBJVjBigvHQ2c5YHK6c\"><strong>【开放条件】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnD35u4FPraZ6n1PZRgUErch\">完成世界纪游剧情《寻物启事》</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcniLQoyWlLp12j6uUkWl4GOd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnZAZFMLQd2JWdM8Dx26FDbg\"><strong>【奖励内容】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YeK1dljkyoPKuuxhAOvcaYa0nGb\"><strong>头像奖励：</strong>「机傀大乱斗」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn3kXYwi1GVUlOHb1pEl1L8b\"><strong>角色</strong><strong>装饰</strong><strong>奖励：</strong>「魔王头套」「蝴蝶结&middot;捏白」「短喵喵腰饰&middot;铅灰」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BMPDdGRtao60Yhx7Dlbcz8Wwns3\"><strong>战术背包消耗品：</strong>「千丝雨&middot;鎏金」「千丝雨&middot;杏黄」「千丝雨&middot;黛蓝」「怦然心动&middot;白樱」「怦然心动&middot;黛蓝」「怦然心动&middot;鎏金」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NA2YdomxxoipcXxm90mcZhEKny5\"><strong>资源奖励：</strong>「虹彩染剂」「委托密函线索」「暮夜的履迹」「移转模块」「武器移转模块」「铜币」「战斗旋律&middot;四」「武器说明书&middot;四」「深红凝珠」「皎皎之民的信物」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RZaHdHs7NovsngxK0pFcd7eqnSc\"><strong>称号奖励：</strong>「机枢派的」「神之一手」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnlZeq3SfSJA3QtSUq6z1Rbh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnWvuUyqVibz7wal3DOhxyCe\"><strong>【活动说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-T8fgdxtF6oHeyhxqzKSc0ooUnPf\">活动分为【公尚的棋局】与【无尽棋局】。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WaOudjB0wohLLixS47rcyEPznyb\">在【公尚的棋局】中会随着活动进度逐渐开启更多棋局，根据棋局中对方的阵容，制定策略部署我方的【拟真机傀】。不同的【拟真机傀】需要花费的【耗能】不同，部署完我方阵容后【拟真机傀】会自行与对方进行战斗。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EIwZdahEboX7t0xcq24cPFkinfg\">在【无尽棋局】中胜利可获得「对局积分」提升段位。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-A1SSdeKAvoBWojx483JcNAOznwd\">参与【公尚的棋局】与【无尽棋局】完成【对弈感悟】可获得更多【拟真机傀】与「符石」提高我方阵容的战斗力。以及可以获得头像、称号以及用于在【公尚赠礼】中兑换各种活动奖励的活动道具「齿轮」。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BYA1dTNuGorSEcx08lVcil2Nn9c\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>",
                ["title1"] = "【机傀大乱斗】活动说明",
