            [1] = {
                ["title1"] = "【委托密函】苏乙委托密函轮换说明",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/密函轮换预告_728x200-苏乙-CH.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"RYyddKgnjoZUbsxfJSxcGw1hnUh\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WT4OdTuhEodIWwxyp7ic6iXLnMe\">\n<div data-page-id=\"RYyddKgnjoZUbsxfJSxcGw1hnUh\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HOtldJm0Do3EOSxAxwAc33RMn2g\">委托密函将于2026年4月7日更新后进行轮换，以下为轮换规则。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HOtldJm0Do3EOSxAxwAc33RMn2g\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WT4OdTuhEodIWwxyp7ic6iXLnMe\">2026年4月7日版本更新后：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XPeAdHzouoWQZXxF7ZVcljYGnNh\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 169, 129);\">「苏乙」「孤雏的羽迹」</span>将替换<span style=\"color: rgb(171, 100, 218);\">「煜明」「罪愆的逆鳞」</span>进入沉浸式戏剧的限时奖励中。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Pq2kdZfteo1YKxxbHqGczM6KnSf\"><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 100, 218);\">「煜明」「罪愆的逆鳞」「鸣金遥」</span>将替换<span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\">「耶尔与奥利弗」「归墟棘轮」「流浪的蔷薇」</span>加入梦魇残声挑战奖励中。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FJkGdrblQoHj8yxa7T7c1tbVnMf\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\">「耶尔与奥利弗」「归墟棘轮」「流浪的蔷薇」</span>将永久加入【委托密函】商店兑换中。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Pq9FdAnxpo2qBvxIs5BcMBIInrg\">特别提醒：本次梦魇残声奖励轮换时间为2026年4月7日更新后（周二），更新后不会重置梦魇残声周奖励次数，若想获取「煜明」「罪愆的逆鳞」「鸣金遥」的狩月人，请根据自身需求安排游玩挑战。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EVnPdRPaVosffqxOr7McJPc0nMf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-YXXod0l4Zo58bpxfP6Vck7UZnFg\">舞台伴奏与推荐属性</h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZT2ndDGMQoy4haxK3pEcAyfRnGf\">随着本次沉浸式戏剧更新，剧目中的【舞台伴奏】与【推荐属性】也会一同进行更新。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AKCVd0qW2oZU0HxFxvjcujE4nCf\">本期推荐属性：<span style=\"color: rgb(171, 100, 218);\">雷属性</span>、<span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">光属性</span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GvavdEZCAo4AhsxeSKhc0uz6n2b\">本期【舞台伴奏】将会轮换一批新的&ldquo;伴奏&rdquo;，以下为【不朽剧目】中部分&ldquo;伴奏&rdquo;：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UKjVdKsJdoA85vx20qMcEyZsnCc\">●【抉择变奏：元素契约】：敌方单位获得选定的元素属性，受到的克制属性伤害提高400%，非克制属性伤害降低50%。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PKT8dS9jXoeyPvxM648cnDbVnFc\">●【活跃急板：辉煌号召】：友方单位施放战技或终结技时，获得昂扬提高15.0%效果，持续12秒，最多叠加5层。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CIT7d7zvvoGTQzxePyNcMFz9ned\">●【活跃急板：俯瞰日记】：滞空期间造成伤害时，获得造成的伤害提高50.0%效果，落地1秒后移除。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Beh9dBhrroz4eZxlrJccHovKnBe\">●【防御变奏：精神淬炼】：敌方单位受到的伤害降低80.0%，每次受到技能伤害时，伤害降低幅度降低4.0%。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AjjUdlt44o5JjfxsWTucdYMKnpf\">●【协调柔板：传福音士】：友方单位技能耐久降低25.0%，技能范围提高75.0%。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BYYodyftGoA7KVxlMjecMLi9nzf\">●【协调柔板：最后一滴血】：友方单位攻击降低150.0%，技能威力提高100%。</div>\n</div>",
                ["language"] = "CN",
                ["title"] = "【委托密函】苏乙委托密函轮换说明",
            },
        },
