        ["Content"] = {
            [1] = {
                ["title1"] = "「皓苍诀」版本更新说明",
                ["body"] = "<div data-page-id=\"EscLd8CDqo8QonxynImcDDrVnHc\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn85bArMF4O3TJ2JiJzlSZJh\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/20250813万能公告-468X192.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"468\" height=\"192\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn85bArMF4O3TJ2JiJzlSZJh\">亲爱的狩月人：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcne5wqK88fMou8SHlbsm8d3g\">感谢您的关注与支持，以下是华胥资料片「皓苍诀」2026年4月7日版本更新说明，辛苦查阅。</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnC2ZrNqhdyAIMkmIHKMRNXe\">✦维护更新说明✦</h3>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcntkcsiSrDgfVDdeCwgpV7Eg\"><strong>◆维护时间◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnmBJAGIhjMaC080RkxXDXzb\">2026年4月7日（星期二）04:00-11:00（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnVJWftyF2IwmlE5j1irAQFd\">*开服时间视维护进度有可能提前或推迟，还请留意公告通知。维护更新期间所有服务器将无法登录，请狩月人合理安排游戏时间。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn7tkTnzlyCWPysEuB1EKNQc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcn3dgLXlrJnlwZWN3pRClA5X\"><strong>◆维护补偿◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnL9Ba9qAEj3afW7HXFQcKgc\">月石*300、委托手册&middot;二*6、委托手册&middot;三*4、玩具气锤*10</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnqTBdWtYb2SH6F615n23FTg\">* 领取条件：解锁【邮件】功能，邮件领取有效时间至2026年4月14日23:59（UTC+8）。</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnHVFPFKrBnl3guOXmFqYlvh\"><strong>◆下架提醒◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-K0Zzdy2Klodb6Xxt02LcR3YpnXd\">以下商品将于2026年4月6日 16:30（UTC+8）下架。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GxmidmNNroMZh6x0bBGck3jCnxd\">【华宴万华礼箱】、【鸣金万华礼箱】、【鸣金万华补给礼箱】、【鸣金装饰补给礼箱】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UgQsd2nwfoUcEuxQxRecZipFnah\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BNGud6D79oXcZ4xuqtPcOwcRngd\">以下商品将于2026年4月6日 17:00（UTC+8）下架。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HnpNdRzUrohLZ4xqWc7cwbngndf\">【外观组合礼箱&middot;匆匆】、【装饰组合礼箱&middot;财源】、【外观组合礼箱&middot;冬日】、【思绪礼箱&middot;煜明】、【交织的思绪&middot;煜明】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ho79d8HdiojGcVx961KczsIinDe\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Bpj8dtOPDojdL3xoTY0cQjCzn5f\">以下活动将于2026年4月6日 17:00（UTC+8）结束，各位狩月人请记得及时领取活动中的奖励。</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RxkOdmKjZoW4H4xGlzOcKFxdnBM\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>活动限定万华：【宴夜诉平生】</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QkzBdUJo2omBqKx8rojcAJj9nWd\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>时装试玩：【山止川行】</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-P06Zd3do5oYHUnx7JJfcUxpnnwg\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>吟游诗集：【晨曦序曲 &middot; Ⅱ】</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RMxYdIfk2oMftcxo2p4cnPp9nzg\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>角色试玩：【沙痕留迹】</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Qjnod5XMiokc5yx8OZact1Z5nRh\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>其他活动：【沉浸式戏剧&middot;煜明】【共游阿特拉西亚】【清平愿】</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Kd8Ndb2tPoRT5nxJMCccTjxnnzh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EOCRdHGHNoFZK1xfhpmcH8njnNb\">在活动限定万华【宴夜诉平生】结束后，以下当期可兑换商品将于2026年4月13日 05:00（UTC+8）下架。</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-D7BBdDyGSoXsDyxnySkcGMa7ndb\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>止流形象：「携金宴夜」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-P3KVdLBgVoUbMGxRxNdcq6Djnpb\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>胜利动作：「悠游水岸」「睥睨山河」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NQbLdLlDQohyIIxDEvyc8mqpnbh\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>展示动作：「睥睨山河」系列、「承露」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ihp4dmBCOoUnswx1A8Ncd6xnnJd\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>武器装饰：「龙渊穗」系列、「龙纹坠」系列</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QuG9dLmHsoR8oQxHJyEcckPWnBb\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>武器形象：「大荒宴」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ANajdAfVVo2w5bxHDAlcACOenxe\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>头部装饰：「诸天月相」系列</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Nj0JdRPxCot0oRxbEv2cVcEDnPh\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>光晕特效：「游龙诀」系列</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IDpJdmilLoyF1Hxngebca5H3nWd\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>足迹特效：「火树银花」系列</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Vk0jdhHwGonULtxImMvcIRZyn6b\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>螺旋飞跃特效：「星河游龙」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KFLYdMUKdoDLzGx3MVVce3wZnsg\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>下落攻击特效：「星落如雨」</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Nhgxdf8VEo6H5wxJRwJcAyvenkh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TYP8dfszZokoMDx8az6c6qxanKd\">以下外观将于2026年4月6日 17:00（UTC+8）下架。</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YZtMdge5DoMml4xZcbXcunGxn1f\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>武器形象：「糖福禄」系列、「碧霄吟」系列</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TRxFdcOI6oIVRvxGqWucCVv8n7c\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>帽子装饰：「釉色铭」、「雨中行」、「致候晴空」、「柔风吹拂」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AmcDdoSsWoc7AixYhGOcN9oUnBf\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>头部装饰：「神行发饰」系列、「星霜王冠」系列、「雀翎发饰」系列、「兔绒发饰」系列</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UjUSdvyeQoIimFxZOYWcCl8BnL4\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>脸部装饰：「炫酷墨镜」系列、「龙纹墨镜」系列、「一线风水」系列、「执理光轮」系列</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Cdn8dvuV1oRhTcxpM9QcKmRcnUb\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>背部装饰 &middot; 上：「鎏金飞羽」系列、「星霜披肩」系列、「雀翎背饰」系列、「执理佩剑」系列、「阴阳玉背饰」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ENCNdjfOPoInK5xO6FncFSoWnlc\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>背部装饰 &middot; 下：「兔绒腰饰」系列、「神行腰饰」系列</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Hcp6d57LFoK6jpxfDH6c5jFInzc\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>腰部装饰：「伏龙节」系列、「墨玉纸伞」系列、「神算子」</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NtDtdazLMomuUaxUziUcc2z7nhf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnLxW0VxVSBJj0G1asMqiwTf\"><strong>◆更新方式◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Qd8mdIQLko0NmCx12kQcqxvpndb\">PC端：重新开启启动器后，点击【更新游戏】，进行更新；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TSVvd2TNJoaAXDxCSSBcnlBqnzb\">安卓端：进入游戏后，根据游戏弹窗提示进行更新；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CPv9d8iWco0zzexOTobc3fuznNe\">iOS端：前往App Store进行更新。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ILqKd0UtPo6XQqxbj5tcW0tTnCh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnxbXmHMQFcJCYZ4unN9SFKb\"><strong>✦</strong><strong>设备要求✦</strong></h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FX3qdmrRsoMt8IxUckScFSV5n4g\">为保证游戏的顺利安装与体验，建议狩月人参考以下配置要求：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QSeldYRuBoSA9XxtfjpcsEsSnCh\"><strong>最低配置</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Y7MVdycDMomPhyxrB3OcGVUhnYf\">Android：系统Android 8及以上、处理器高通骁龙 845/天玑1000以上、运行内存8GB以上、可用存储空间20GB以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HEYCdRztkoT3ctxKADCch1trngh\">iOS：iPhone 12以上型号、系统版本iOS 15.0以上、可用存储空间20G以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Z5fSdL1hMo7Y7jxdLqIcbtGanJf\">PC：系统Windows 10 64bit以上、处理器Intel Core i5(第九代) /AMD Ryzen 5 2600X以上、显卡Geforce GTX1060/AMD Radeon RX 580以上、运行内存16GB以上、可用存储空间40G以上。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IqITdAAxQoG2grx3t32cfOu9nHf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HUaVd2X05o6WvdxJ1FqcDocTn0g\"><strong>推荐配置</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VXMEd4PavosnBixkgBickcuKn1d\">Android：系统Android 12、处理器高通骁龙 8Gen 1/ 天玑 9000、内存12GB 以上、可用存储空间20GB 以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-K0QCdfxrFoMrtQxRQPFckFCDnFg\">iOS：机型iPhone 14 Pro、系统iOS 17.0、可用存储空间20GB及以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Zm9ldsL7mo4B9OxzY5JcewrunOh\">PC：系统Windows 10 64bit、处理器:Intel core i7(第十代)/AMD Ryzen 7 3700x、显卡GeForce RTX 2060/AMD Radeon RX5700XT、运行内存32GB及以上、预留硬盘空间：40GB及以上。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CctSdQX0voBdwOx00Accpm4Pnce\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Y8WEd2mq0oN1KwxZFIRcAfn6nUh\"><strong>手柄支持</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Lma8dLdqZoF5PJxfilWcweAknwd\">目前《二重螺旋》于PC设备支持以下有线/无线控制器。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-J24Zd9Vnho9NgBxYkDqcugwHnke\">Xbox：Xbox系列、Xbox Elite系列</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PjUYdjKNwoKzj7xE2ogcw4yZnlh\">Playstation&reg;：DualSense&reg;、DualSense Edge&trade;、DUALSHOCK&reg;4</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EJijdZYDDomL83xXib8cdnB0nSf\">*使用DualSense&reg;或DUALSHOCK&reg;4控制器在PC端进行体验时，推荐您采用有线连接方式以获得最佳游玩体验。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZlQudSlXno1wu5x5xpOcabDAnHb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcncwxj8y5MxODJHDcdaNQ8Kg\"><strong>✦版本全新内容 ✦</strong></h3>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnwDxhuEurzoiVHKMX9h9k73\"><strong>◆全新剧情任务开放◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BN9PdWGV6ohM1zxegiNc1YMPnrd\">✦ 主线剧情更新：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UPPnd74PhoEnyWxaGiic8R1nnuf\">「大风起处问皓苍」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UJG1dl9gZoZG5mxqyGJcPQNSnXf\">\"人永远能够挣脱所谓的宿命和计划，创造出新的意外。&rdquo;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GFBhdR7iFomG9hxABxncrOECnPg\">【开放时间】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HTwed2gWyoNMpsxF8l8coAVinre\">2026年4月7日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LyFpdAFbioelc9xCYIucjwJdnGe\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HT9ed5gcQohF2Px9cDjcN7yAnff\">✦ 支线剧情更新：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-W6lEd8B9woWzTuxMZdXcIEgdnSd\">「若言琴上有琴声」，「忘川回响」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-H7lLdT88PoQhVVx5n9LclBFXnze\">清晨阳光照在了高悬的执律阁顶，又逐渐照亮了胡同食肆，照亮了祀烟阁前香炉袅袅升起的烟。沿街的叫卖声，巷口的谈笑声，鸽群掠过的振翅声交织成一片。今日也是皓京城中熙熙攘攘的一天。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MXyBdzBB6oVumwxmG2ncYikknEg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QKAjd7Ul1oZQQsxSxlqc9Qy9n5g\">【开放时间】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XsHTdBB0coGXWaxX2JTcpLESn4d\">2026年4月16日（UTC+8）起长期开放</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OIzEdhkgsoj2ttxSB5XckBc4nEv\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-L0KSd4OK5ovzzRxDbwfcVEovn1p\">✦ 活动剧情更新：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QQVEd7DFPoOBpExPVYbc7uVfnXf\">「奉香群英试」 在这场既为了抚慰人心，又为了探索变革之路的&ldquo;奉香群英试&rdquo;上，你看到了一个熟悉的青碧色身影 &mdash;&mdash; 与苏乙联手完成争锋赛事吧。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-W5DJdBDwNoxtmexxbL1cmoJonjd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BmIzdDUhYoeXbOxGZ9PcjsDDnwc\">【开放时间】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Zsy4dRufAoPkgIx6XqVcaTXjneg\">2026年4月23日10:00（UTC+8）后长期开放</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-X5wDdCeJIobnfoxoJuKcnVoInJh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Xgv0d9MRlosRXRxlK22co1ADnOh\">✦ 光阴集更新：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-O6axdt5aDoITjsxrz1acivZrnfd\">「光阴集&middot;苏乙」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OnaGdOFEwoCaCmxhea4cesgBnye\">飘零的叶子落了地，飘零的人也回家去。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-S2KKdDOQ4oM6BqxVHnicygJpnte\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-X8nZduTBnoSqWHxf4Uxcj4K3nMg\">「光阴集&middot;止流」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ko2OdAK4LoL6FUx4DlXcI7dFnRe\">道可道，非常道。支撑万事万物运转的，往往是不可言明之道。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RcqldYvgVo2cgjxkSUhcf1JynWe\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VYdkddZ58oNbsqxMysncv4RenCc\">「光阴集&middot;煜明」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JVz0d7zdEogCKUxDrC5cyZLGnch\">悠远的笛声随风而逝，与之一同消散的，还有苦涩与欢欣交织的过往。</div>\n<div class=\"ace