ZddfuroyIX6xvFYXcSFpTnrc\">版本期间限时上架，首次购买优惠价「月石晶胚」*780；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CwA7d94eXoFXcjxU7czcqnIKnX6\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Zym2dP30Uob7OqxffACcgutInl9\">◆【<strong>狩月人形象礼箱&middot;不羁</strong>】上架</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Sc4sdadTuoFwzDxskl4c9XtOnch\">版本期间限时上架，6元可得！</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-K9mbd61s3ogPKwxoDDNcx5ainwe\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QMJ2dbikZo7hgdxknxUc72Qxndg\"><strong>◆【外观组合礼箱&middot;不羁】上架</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-W2ThdWAjrog7wxxIHP8crxcYnzf\">购买后可获得「自选形象礼箱&middot;不羁」以及「羽毛笔&middot;墨玉」「轻抚&middot;涅白」「头像框&middot;失色烈火」装饰。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WUjfdFvUiolK1axyd95c1eYynmd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KsG9dBEpNobzu3xVqp4ciit8neT\">◆<strong>【千丝雨惊喜礼箱】上架</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Y6ZBdx7rjoUdxYx7lz0crsWDnCe\">千丝雨惊喜礼箱每日限购1个，售价1元。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PwYVdn5gOo8oulx1xUHcBIeRnyi\">购买后可获得「千丝雨」*1，同时还会获得额外随机获得10~888月石晶胚。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WYwxdtS2Rox1eFxHj99cgObdnze\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MfMEdkvKdo7vEFxsVcochCbznBb\">◆【<strong>风息万华系列礼箱</strong>】上架</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Kvb1dIstPoZ4z3xrIc2clpHCnsH\">活动期间【商店】将上架「风息装饰万华礼箱」、「风息万华补给礼箱」、「风息万华礼箱」、「风息万华周礼箱」；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PBFQdUk0boNCoyx227NcLE7Rnlf\">购买以下礼包将额外获得《云&middot;二重螺旋》畅玩卡时长：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IuN6dtnoCoTOXNxBB8fcWdSIn0Y\">「风息装饰万华礼箱&middot;一」：赠3天畅玩卡 「风息装饰万华礼箱&middot;二」：赠7天畅玩卡</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ds2bdNmcgoccoBxBTRlcnb7MnRl\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZJs8dpiqoo0GlLxPhY4c68Shn4b\">*更多说明请前往游戏内查阅；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-U0T8dw3Jwo0J9yxG4vAcmqWGn2g\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WtPWdrAhho6bysxP9YictqbunZg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnoh4FRuKWmFgk5X66rJbQwh\"><strong>◆全新功能开放◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnFLqfxpbt9sBwSs6g1lIYOd\">✦ 新增分包下载功能，拥有基础资源即可进行游戏，传送至未下载场景时触发资源包下载；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IX6ZdJcSzo2LnexqklCcLLlbn6d\">✦ 新增角色溯源等级上限，海尔法、丽蓓卡为首批开放溯源等级上限角色；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FSUudtwMDoCfhBxyodocPMaEnAh\">✦ 新增魔之楔装配页面大数据推荐功能；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VsR3d9pPWogCjlxetbic17ifn8b\">✦ 新增二级密码功能，可在【设置-其他】中开启，进行解锁、商城送礼、消耗金色品质/潜质魔灵、熔炼武器等操作时，需要进行密码验证；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GSdbde1GAoQyuKxeVj3cE9SwnVe\">✦ 【设置 - 控制】页面新增射击时镜头距离切换；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CnLldOuNXoED3ixOcZscD5rinPd\">✦ 【设置 - 其他】页面新增剧情中是否使用主角外观的开关；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XR9jdCuGxo0fUrxMv8ac8pZDnCg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnsU78dA4r4Rfv1eaX9QnmDg\"><strong>◆</strong><strong>其他内容更新</strong><strong>◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KouzdBffnoVWr8xLDCBcZgXOnPx\">✦ 新增手机端抖音录制功能，点击按钮即可开始录屏；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TCJhd0oRfoI4XVxLoJwc9X4jn8e\">✦ 新增魔灵潜质：装备此潜质时，副本撤离点生成后，释放魔灵支援技能将直接传送至撤离点；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CiBGd2o1ao2c3lxfGSMc0ngdnC2\">✦ 新增魔灵潜质：装备此潜质时，可吸取范围内掉落物品；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-H4tXdhcrgo6gkixPWIRcLyXFnCd\">✦ 新增游戏窗口化置顶功能；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MJqmd9QifoJtuJx8gGBcOYI4nzq\">✦ 新增【悬赏委托】-【争衡】；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QhBMdD5NOoLrqOx3bdfcOtN6ngf\">✦ 新增【悬赏委托】难度V副本；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ISfcdyOWxoTQlaxCZoaco3YknWg\">✦ 更新登录界面视频；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AJc4d6Om6okOGfxMZ0Wc9XF6nte\">✦ 新增副本结算界面添加好友功能；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KkeRdiap2oPirbxMSgDcFbo6nch\">✦ 新增止流、煜明、苏乙、卡米拉【停驻光阴】相关成就；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DBZmdtHcJo1Jxuxc7iucoGdXnef\">✦【百科】系统新增词条分类：故事。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-C1eqdWDMFosYkpxsTY4cNN02n5e\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnZBw4sAzgJZvKNEBYaZH5Hc\"><strong>✦版本优化内容 ✦</strong></h3>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnx7o1rvp9LpvzBmWANBoebc\"><strong>◆系统◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZZfjdBi5coCFqkx9lccclDprnNb\">✦ 优化了【整备 - 查看属性说明】页面，支持手柄滚动查看；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LKh7dcv7ooxvJ4xNicUcWS2cnGq\">✦ 优化了【整备】中的通用主题皮肤自选包界面，持有对应道具时，支持购买/使用该道具；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-N2e6dtReco4sQtxLeNWc4Zhsnzo\">✦ 优化了【吟游诗集】购买体验，临近结束时购买新增二次确认弹窗；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FK9YdJj25op7yFxsH2icJMFmnrg\">✦ 优化了自选包类型道具的预览方式，点击道具 - 头像【预览】按钮即可直接预览；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DwMXdleEgorEE8xWZ4FcLCajn0g\">✦ 优化了角色试玩副本中的任务栏；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NKGGddkhOoGUdwxIUipcfI6enxh\">✦ 优化了魔灵界面，支持直接预览技能等级效果；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Sq7odcwGGoznycxsT4yck5kkn2g\">✦ 个人主页界面新增【狩月人之阶】按钮，点击打开【历史排名】界面，可查看该玩家在之前【狩月人之阶巅峰排名】中的信息；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JhqDd1vaFoA4QdxN1oJccYeYn1g\">✦ 优化了声望系统的视觉体验，调整了部分界面UI布局；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WdkudTooConWjhx56TnchIyrnId\">✦ PC端密函选择界面等通用弹窗按钮支持绑定快捷键；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OQPideeX7oEU9ex2HxjcoLKbnBc\">✦ 优化了联机匹配系统，局内可添加/接受好友、实时聊天；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WNCJdQnUGoL3lYx9DzncibjPnTb\">✦ 优化了聊天系统，增加了区域、世界频道切换功能；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UxmNdCHb0oB6vTxICNUcFnK6nAg\">✦ 优化了聊天系统，调整了部分界面的UI布局；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OZ4BdwLIZoG95HxHr5hcumdqn3b\">✦ 优化了联系匹配系统，调整了界面的视觉，新增消极处罚提示；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WVUGdshMnoFOqPxtj6wcZ8RNncX\">✦ 优化了魔之楔增幅系统，新增了下一级的效果预览；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E1DcdoYnUobTUKxrxBZcGfqWnVb\">✦ 优化了【万华】系统中，寻觅道具后的视觉效果；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ib5NdJYjEoekYqxesfmc0qHpnvg\">✦ 优化了商店委托密函购买界面，二次确认弹窗中新增显示已有数量、溯源等级和熔炼等级；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XrQXd6PKHoKhP1xnIDucaDoFnGh\">✦ 优化了【铸造列表】的视觉效果；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XqyPdE9IuodWz6xh0n1cKpqxn5f\">✦ 优化了【夜航手册】的等级栏间距；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EsILdES5hoFc1XxqXljcE42DnGd\">✦ 优化了【迷津 - 翻阅手记】界面的视觉效果；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Zi9rdPHtCohlFxxThhsc5H4VnTh\">✦ 优化了【鱼类图鉴】界面的视觉效果；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DuggdSBDVoPgWbxVOI0cHNLknEe\">✦ 优化了【整备】界面左下角侧方选择的视觉弹窗；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RMlQdpscBo5yYJxmmEpc1iFdnId\">✦ 优化了【外观预览】界面的视觉布局；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QFe8d6GlpozmHaxqH4BcvbsTnrf\">✦ 优化了【迷津-难度选择】界面的视觉效果；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Q5ixdl5xfomwVLxAONic6XSvnGf\">✦ 优化了联机举报系统，被拉黑玩家将不会再次匹配；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JGbqdMEsrotFKexvzkwcnzKGnqe\">✦ 优化了公告系统的视觉效果，由弹窗形态调整为全屏页面；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZZpudjO5hoNNevxlIeNcVrJynQe\">✦ 优化了自动补领弹窗的相关提示文案；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-R61UdraESoiX7PxdG8WcTS0wnic\">✦ 优化了角色动作的性能消耗；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DMUVdjuqXoIPLjxg0vFcpmDRngY\">✦ 优化了任务栏界面的视觉效果；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MzGKdyrcZopnxsx59JDcv6YAnKd\">✦ 优化了成就界面的视觉效果；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-D4Uid6kh3oEtTIxiaIFcPHOrnsf\">✦ 优化了商店推荐页的视觉效果。</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-YeTYdJKItoHTOmxHRWEcPw3Ynuh\"><strong>◆玩法◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PMQAdlP7Fo1GZ4xVBd9cx5KZnrf\">✦ 优化了冰湖城部分怪物的难度，由精英怪调整为非精英怪；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZybadyvKuo4cwgxphqxcDjpunfc\">✦ 优化了序章【前往山上的遗迹】的任务体验：目标击杀数从10个下调至3个，击杀期间怪物不再新增；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IfFAdDGGSogErnxqMUqcknO2nAg\">✦ 优化了序章【净界岛】的场景美术效果；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-J8RbdnUhXoxIbpxahDocVW4VnXd\">✦ 优化了移动端螺旋飞跃操作，长按按钮支持调整镜头视角；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CuTPdagjRot4syxGBJbcOjxdngb\">✦ 优化了丽蓓卡在作为协战同伴时的战斗逻辑，现在释放【缠绵之触】的索敌范围将更大；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WN5ydao7SoSCkNxaLevc24munVe\">✦ 优化了琳恩在作为协战同伴时的战斗逻辑，现在释放【火药酬宾】后的索敌将更加精准。</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-EVTgd7ThtokZfDxJWEacm4Obn0f\"><strong>◆其他问题◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HmNMd3wH5oxcj5xvT1KcIFP6nkb\">✦ 优化了法语输入法下的游玩体验；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LoNodRNZCoPFs3xltmPciNhvnIo\">✦ 优化了冰湖城东区灯光的性能消耗；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RV7JdbbiooAhQsx5Z1WcaxSGnkh\">✦ 优化了法语语言下部分文本的文案；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-L7HodMHaNoDNBhx6VLgcqREPnTh\">✦ 优化了双Boss血条，移除中断文字提示，一方死亡即中断UI；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DhlAdeakDoEUQWxwYewcnhqCnve\">✦ 优化了日语汉字上标注音的显示效果，新增了部分支持上标显示的界面；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AwIOdpXrnoafW7x3t84cGkAgn4g\">✦ 优化了移动端自定义功能，新手引导、new提示、技能量谱等支持自定义设置；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HlfodkpeKom3CFxmjwLc1RJLnjg\">✦ 优化了移动端自定义功能，支持多套方案保存，可直接试用当前方案；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-X4P7dCuhpomVUExOAUvcYEPhnvf\">✦ 优化了移动端锁定操作功能，按住移动摇杆后，滑至【自动移动提示按钮】区域后松开触发锁定操作；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KBSAdNKgXocjVEx0T1hciZ6Fn0d\">✦ 优化了暴击数字的视觉效果；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OPA1dyxGMoHkr1xMDTtcBFUpn6W\">✦ 优化了精英怪血条的视觉效果；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QVHvdw2m5oYCaCxKlaKcGiBJnog\">✦ 优化了部分剧情的演出表现；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E7rRdHnKToaXF6xil4QcXYThnuc\">✦ 优化了安卓设备着色器编译阶段时长。</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnXnd4CB9i2iKhA6BwSBYnfg\"><strong>✦版本修复内容✦</strong></h3>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnXi7LqmPvybG32zr6v2PZIf\"><strong>◆</strong><strong>角色</strong><strong>◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VrWydtknGoqlFWxgSj9cljETnrg\">✦ 修复了部分角色中结算界面镜头显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-V5OmdjuQAoaY94x0rd0cpp06nBb\">✦ 修复了在部分剧情中，角色显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PT4qdrnrUoXuLRxoWFgczrlkndb\">✦ 修复了主角在使用双刀进行攻击时，攻击特效的虚影显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OYLDdDz5Doef4vxznlUcS2jpnNe\">✦ 修复了煜明部分技能特效显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OR6kdBfypoMl07xBOBccMQ92nSd\">✦ 修复了煜明在下落攻击到一些不平整地面时无法释放【濯暗鳞】的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KgyCdp603osu3xxVNgScmwhZnsb\">✦ 修复了在赛琪在使用【腐草为萤】后立即使用【抽茧成梦】移动的方向不受方向键控制的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HNxidgjPToIML8x3PlzcY62XnMb\">✦ 修复了在移动端使用松露骑乘【榛子】进行冲刺时，结束镜头显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZcMQdnPpwoZM7xxOFuZcopAUnHb\">✦ 修复了在联机时，莉兹贝尔蓄力状态下，武器未按正常情况变大的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GUGwdA9PSoC4udxRLa6cCvXEnmd\">✦ 修复了在联机时，刻舟的被动效果有概率不显示的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RJbJdWbOtoc5CzxFDTmcczROn7d\">✦ 修复了贝蕾妮卡、扶疏档案中的部分文本错误。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QsAGdmtJ7oYJ8txBL7jcv2wDnXf\">✦ 调整了刻舟第六溯源的文本描述，使其描述更加准确。（实际效果与更新前一致）</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-OgiadoYnWoMvbYxAQnac38ranTe\">◆玩法◆</h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GEYHdrNhBoCDBWxmVqvcU6Qwngd\">✦ 修复了部分武器装饰特效显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GGz3dIOdEo414Fx6RydcxzX0nWb\">✦ 修复了部分武器装饰无法正常预览的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WSBtdRxOroH2tDxXCA2cWP2nnZe\">✦ 修复了任务【海的另一边】有概率开启宝箱未出现任务道具，导致任务无法完成的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-U2ycdah0LogjEfxJsdRc8GtKnYg\">✦ 修复了在声名系统中切换讨伐页签中的目标，但难度选择未重置的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TWItdExYSoOijexvSMJcswNqnhh\">✦ 修复了在声名系统中领完去讨伐奖励后，难度图标未正常打勾的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-J7lPdnRrvoMsqyxZnw9ctK5rnme\">✦ 修复了在声名系统中完成任务后，同等难度的任务按钮状态显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JBNbdSgpAoUa3txya6QcfeabnCg\">✦ 修复了在移动端魔之楔「水雾弥散」部分效果未生效的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YSHrdQoA7ouNdexZmGMcAFWanlc\">✦ 修复了在进行多轮次委托后，有概率无法拾取掉落物的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Fl3DdgfUSoccu2xCoUTcRCz0nYg\">✦ 修复了在使用冲刺时与座椅交互，有概率会使角色坐下位置偏移的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RYyYdBGygoVCiLx1EHocEpIInTg\">✦ 修复了探险委托Lv10在角色站在特定位置后，怪物的移动会上下抽搐的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ItIRd7lhTojS8ux1Ny3cO4IXnEh\">✦ 修复了部分钓鱼点，在钓到鱼时水面上钩特效显示不明显的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XmyqdPkSaoDkbTx761Zc4NfAnnc\">✦ 修复了任务【海的另一边】在钓鱼事件中进行了多次钓鱼，有概率导致任务无法完成的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QH8cdf3qnotySUxxe4VchIQ2ned\">✦ 修复了【竞逐 I】中，BOSS会瞬间移动的问题</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VjOEdTWbfooavgxi0zZcmkovnuh\">✦ 修复了移动端部分玩家【梦魇残声-炼火的典狱长】副本中，开局异常掉落的问题</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VqkHd4uOvorJQBxuuz4cV5c2nrd\">✦ 修复了动作兼容性，解决部分动作下配饰自定义的旋转异常的问题</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OCmCdZwfkoP0vDxQ0pxcUJeVnie\">✦ 调整了部分夜航手册的委托等级，原先80级的委托降低至75级。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GQnodPMH5ovHWnxleVbcxWaunDe\">✦ 调整了武器「流浪的蔷薇」的被动描述文本。（实际效果无调整）</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-MC3ZdGy1KoydVRxYyLAcib0Hnob\">◆系统◆</h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UPRIdxO0To59eVxotUecO3eSnse\">✦ 修复了在部分情况下，背包中的道具选中状态显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CDUKdIE98o5OELxMwANcqnbpn7c\">✦ 修复了营救人质委托中，人质在死亡后倒计时未消失的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BNjZddIBCoATBixDKP4cPZcNn9f\">✦ 修复了部分角色整备界面图标显示不全的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XrdrdKvRsolCLbxHkC3cWRB8nxb\">✦ 修复了在领取突破奖励时，若存在多个可领取的奖励，只领取其中一个，其余可领取奖励状态显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RfTidcuutoR7THxZsjWcTjOPndE\">✦ 修复了夜航手册50级奖励预览异常显示了首通奖励的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E7wDdleLuoxscGxXbppcpT7TnBb\">✦ 修复了在部分机型的移动端下，历练界面中白的位置错误的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DiEtdt5nToTFVpxHTCWceQYUnUg\">✦ 修复了在移动端钓鱼时额外奖励会和界面中的点击空白区域提示词重叠的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Wu4wda0UzouuLbx3RdqciGmenbb\">✦ 修复了在联机时，有狩月人进入撤离点后再出来，后续其他狩月人进入撤离点时的显示有概率显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZzSod4mSToVX5NxCt2JcLWUsn5g\">✦ 修复了在未达到夜航手册的进入等级的情况下，可以通过图鉴中的获取途径进入夜航手册副本的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UTCYdSBJVolOINx9LDoc5vhHnbh\">✦ 修复了在一次性铸造多个物品，在锻造途中取消，显示获得的物品数量与实际获得的不一致的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EZMCd8b5EovdLCxjnO2cl6Iun7g\">✦ 修复了在夜航手册委托结束后，有概率会出现&ldquo;历练不可用&rdquo;的提示的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NhqUdfaSZowhIRxK9c3cuvzOnbi\">✦ 调整了部分声名任务中，完成条件不清晰的描述。（实际完成条件与更新前一致）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-G1GHdGwR2oWvfoxztvBcefFZnqL\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-GdibdRYu8ouRjYxTsZzcbVZqn9d\">◆其他问题◆</h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Hn3tdZP60oyoynxJGFpcsuLNnnd\">✦ 修复了部分场景模型缺失可以走出地图外的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OlXFdvdKXorYMhxZbZRcRrLJnZg\">✦ 修复了格雷姆废矿部分区域斜坡移动不畅的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-I8UodAALIorsWVxVnu2cASYNn7b\">✦ 修复了在使用网页云游戏首次进入游戏时分辨率显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NSfedECK3oRoe2xqk6NcTLGsn6e\">✦ 修复了部分剧情场景中NPC动作异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EKQ9d7qv8o5IH1xjLEzcedOOn5c\">✦ 修复了净界岛区域部分场景的材质显示异常的问题。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-T0hFdcDEbofTEqxdiPocOElNndc\">✦ 调整了净界岛地区神秘遗迹中层区域的水池的深度。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FsAGd53bqowGwWxqAZrcIkjTnmb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnISip1wR5ucOz29kiGIBmFh\">《二重螺旋》运营团队</div>\n</div>",
