        ["Content"] = {
            [1] = {
                ["language"] = "CN",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/1.2二创头图.JPEG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1404\" height=\"256\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"X6HEdG9ILosrHwxTqIFcRdJknhd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\" old-record-id-doxcnVYB5iGz3f3KFN13PR9wTuf\">「大风歌&middot;下」创作激励计划开启！奖金&amp;游戏道具助力创作，期待各位狩月人的参与~</div>\n<div class=\" old-record-id-doxcnVYB5iGz3f3KFN13PR9wTuf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\" old-record-id-doxcnVYB5iGz3f3KFN13PR9wTuf\">\n<div data-page-id=\"X6HEdG9ILosrHwxTqIFcRdJknhd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcniQNpcVqZsxA7NfTFJ9ST7d\"><strong>B站：</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnGsraB7WQ9rZHnbCzRpKklg\">登录哔哩哔哩平台，携带话题<strong>#二重螺旋创作者激励计划#</strong>参与投稿，或在<strong>【二重螺旋】</strong>专区下进行直播，满足相应条件即可参与现金瓜分，还有丰厚的月石晶胚奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnGsraB7WQ9rZHnbCzRpKklg\">PC端：<a href=\"https://live.bilibili.com/blackboard/era/LyPkRBJmgn4PYnrL.html\">&gt;&gt;点击参与&lt;&lt;</a></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnGsraB7WQ9rZHnbCzRpKklg\">移动端：<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/era/F0DRaqKxKIyWmahe.html?auto_media_playback=1\">&gt;&gt;点击参与&lt;&lt;</a></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnGsraB7WQ9rZHnbCzRpKklg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnGsraB7WQ9rZHnbCzRpKklg\"><strong>抖音：</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnGsraB7WQ9rZHnbCzRpKklg\">\n<div data-page-id=\"X6HEdG9ILosrHwxTqIFcRdJknhd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\" old-record-id-doxcnXnGzAawk0l7zSS7K3RA073\">前往抖音搜索<strong>&ldquo;二重螺旋&rdquo;</strong>进入二重螺旋官号主页，参与创作激励活动，投稿视频即有机会赢取现金奖励！</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
